Definition: a man who is the lover of a man or woman
Example: if I'd known he was her boyfriend I wouldn't have asked; When the law changed, Pet could finally married his long-time boyfriend Jim
Synonyms: fellow, beau, swain, man, lover, a, who, is, the, of, or, woman, if, I, d, known, he, was, her, wouldn, t, have, asked, When, law, changed, Pet, could, finally, married, his, long-time, Jim
Category: noun.person
